Implemented:
- Pokemon index with pagination
- Pokemon search, by name and types
- Detailed pokemon view (with very minimal info)
- Favourite and unfavourite pokemon (in pokemon detailed view)
- Favourite pokemon list page
- Postgresql database
- For styling used vanilla CSS Simple.css framework (https://simplecss.org/)
- Docker compose setup

Setup:

docker compose up

(get inside pokemon_web-php container)

docker exec -it CHANGE_ME /bin/bash 

php bin/console doctrine:database:create

php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate

php bin/console app:cache-pokemon